  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the efficacy, safety, and cost-effectiveness of lower
      calorie refeeding versus higher calorie refeeding in hospitalized adolescents with anorexia
      nervosa.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
